The remote will come in several designs: two will have different fruit or vegetable shapes , one of which will feature speech recognition in lieu of a large number of buttons.
There will also be a child-friendly banana-shaped remote.
Both the company name and slogan will appear on the remote.
The remotes will be bundled with a yellow charging stand.
The devices were made with a latex product with a rubbery texture.
It was decided that the product had met enough of the initial project goals to be launched on the market.
